			</h1>
										<div class="comments-link">
					<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=761#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignleft"><a href="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/?page_id=90"><img src="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ML-Audio-Cover-sm.png" alt="" class="wp-image-762" srcset="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ML-Audio-Cover-sm.png 216w, http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ML-Audio-Cover-sm-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 216px) 100vw, 216px" /></a></figure></div>



<p>The audio version of <a href="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/?page_id=90">Martial Law</a> is now available through <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Audible.com (opens in a new tab)" href="https://www.audible.com/pd/B07MB6G46G/?source_code=AUDFPWS0223189MWT-BK-ACX0-138410&amp;ref=acx_bty_BK_ACX0_138410_rh_us" target="_blank">Audible.com</a>.</p>



<p>This is Book Two in the Times of Turmoil series, and was read once again by my son Seth. </p>



<p>The next two books in the series are being recorded, and we hope to have them available soon.</p>
