						<h1 class="entry-title">
				<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=734" rel="bookmark">Evading Babylon now available as audio book</a>
			</h1>
										<div class="comments-link">
					<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=734#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>I&#8217;m happy to announce that the audio version of my novel <a href="http://cdaybell.com/?page_id=84">Evading Babylon</a> is now available through <a href="https://www.audible.com/pd/B07FTT1ZHN/?source_code=AUDFPWS0223189MWT-BK-ACX0-122921&amp;ref=acx_bty_BK_ACX0_122921_rh_us" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}" data-lynx-mode="asynclazy">Audible.com.</a></p>
<p>This is Book One in the Times of Turmoil series, and was read by my talented son Seth. We will soon have the other volumes of the series completed as well!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.audible.com/pd/B07FTT1ZHN/?source_code=AUDFPWS0223189MWT-BK-ACX0-122921&amp;ref=acx_bty_BK_ACX0_122921_rh_us"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-735 alignleft" src="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/EB-Audio-Coverai-01.jpg" alt="" width="216" height="216" srcset="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/EB-Audio-Coverai-01.jpg 216w, http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/EB-Audio-Coverai-01-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 216px) 100vw, 216px" /></a></p>
