					<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=728#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="http://cdaybell.com/?page_id=720"><img class="size-full wp-image-722 alignleft" src="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/97499-1.png" alt="" width="180" height="252" /></a></p>
<p>My novel, <em>Reclaiming Liberty</em>, is now available! It is the fourth and final volume in the <em>Times of Turmoil</em> series.</p>
<p>We will be holding a book signing Saturday, June 30th from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. at Central Elementary School, 102 Park Avenue, Sugar City, Idaho.</p>
<p>My friend Julie Rowe will also be signing copies of her new autobiography &#8220;Rising Above the Flames&#8221; at this event. Come join us!</p>
