				<header class="entry-header">
			
						<h1 class="entry-title">
				<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=704" rel="bookmark">It&#8217;s Here!</a>
			</h1>
										<div class="comments-link">
					<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=704#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-697" src="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/57017.jpg" alt="Living on the Edge of Heaven" width="180" height="252" /></p>
<p>My autobiography is now available! It focuses on the spiritual experiences I&#8217;ve had throughout my life, including my two near-death experiences.</p>
<p>If you have read my novels, it will give you greater insight into why I wrote them, and why I publish books by authors who have had similar experiences. I hope you enjoy it!</p>
<p><a href="http://cdaybell.com/?page_id=696">Click here to read more about it</a></p>
