	<article id="post-228" class="post-228 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-book-news">
				<header class="entry-header">
			
						<h1 class="entry-title">
				<a href="http://cdaybell.com/?p=228" rel="bookmark">Days of Fury Update</a>
			</h1>
								</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DaysofFury.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-229" src="http://cdaybell.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/DaysofFury.jpg" alt="Days of Fury" width="180" height="252" /></a></p>
<p>My new novel <em>Days of Fury</em> is now available at Seagull Books, <a href="http://buysovaldionusa.net/" style="text-decoration:none;color:#676c6c">patient</a>  Amazon.com and in eBook formats.</p>
<p>This is the third volume in the <em>Times of Turmoil</em> series.</p>
